App      :parama_satya
Version  :1.0.0
Tech     :modular HTML
Created  :mochmona.developer
style    :DRY,SOLID,KISS,Reusable pure component


# ERD,Hirarcy
index.html,style.css,main.js type="module".

index.html (<div id='root')
style.css  (as global style)
main.js    (as Module and core script)

appLayout.js    # as main layout
          |
          |<header>
          |<main>       #container for components
          |<footer>

components/     # as directory for layout and logic component
          |Navigation/Nav.js
          |Sections/section_1.js...etc
          |404.js

pages/    |page-1
          |page-2
          |page-3
utils/          # reusable code and share functionality script
data/api        # optional , dummy data and different API 


!Note : handle async carefully,fecth API ,async Components(callstack,callback que,browser API)
!remember JS : FILO(first in last out) or Last in First Out



